'''Coruscant Global Newsgrid''' was a major news agency based on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. Its programming focused primarily on local Coruscanti news as well as relevant [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] issues and government happenings. In [[16 ABY/Legends|16 ABY]], it was one of the first agencies to display footage of [[Aramadia (Aramadia-class)|''Aramadia'']]<nowiki>'</nowiki>s violent take off when [[Nil Spaar]] fled Coruscant. It also made a report that [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]] had resigned as president of the New Republic, which was false.

[[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] asked the newsgrid's home office for information on [[Akanah Norand Goss Pell]], [[Andras Pell]], and [[Isela Talsava Norand]].<ref name="Shield of Lies">''[[Shield of Lies]]''</ref>

